title: American Horror Story 1984 Breaking July News
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: It would be great if we could get Jamie Lee to come to AHS. She was great in Scream Queens playing against Emma Roberts.
I really hope Idina Porter returns as an actual main cast member this season. I’d also love to see Billie Lourd and Cody Fern return along with Frances Conroy.
So excited, Ryan Murphy is giving me the best birthday gift this year by premiering the new season on my birthday!
Mary, your premise for 1984 is soooo good! I hope it's exactly that! It'd be a newish formula for a season and could be really fun! Great job!
I love you babe. ❤️ So very excited for this next season. The Sarah thing is dramatically depressing.
